                        Ch 1: 3b; Ch 2: 3b; Ch 3: 16a; Ch 4: 18a; Ch 5: 21a; Ch 6: 25a; Ch 7: 29a; Ch 8: 31b; Ch 9: 32b; Ch 10: 34a; Ch 11: 35b; Ch 12: 38a.
                        </summary>  
                           
